# CHANGELOG

## v0.1.0 Initial release by [kivy-garden](https://github.com/kivy-garden/graph)

- Added the demo flower project.

## Additions by [HoerTech-gGmbH](https://github.com/HoerTech-gGmbH/kivy-garden-graph)

### New Features

- **Custom Tick Labels**: Added support for custom tick label strings with error handling for mismatched list sizes
- **Custom Tick Positions**: Implemented ability to set custom tick positions
- **Legend Support**: Added comprehensive legend functionality with dedicated `GraphLegend` class
- **LineAndMarkerPlot Class**: Created new `LineAndMarkerPlot` class with `legend_display` property
- **Axis Reversal**: Automatic axis reversal in linear mode when xmin > xmax or ymin > ymax

### Improvements

- **Color System**: Migrated to `ColorProperty` for plot colors
- **Label Formatting**: Enhanced label options for ticks and legends
- **Y-Label Alignment**: Right-aligned y-axis labels for better readability
- **Marker Size Validation**: Added minimum value constraint for marker sizes

### Bug Fixes

- Fixed error when setting xlabel or ylabel before other properties
- Improved legend cleanup when resetting legends
- Enhanced error handling for mismatched list sizes in custom tick labels

### Technical Changes

- Removed font_size parameter from certain components
- Updated project URL in setup.py
- Improved legend recreation and cleanup mechanisms

## Additions of this fork (v0.4.2.dev0)

### New Features

- **OptimizedSmoothLinePlot**: an optimized SmoothLinePlot implementation for real-time plotting, featuring:
  - Configurable anti-aliasing
  - Automatic buffer management
  - Memory leak prevention
  - Performance optimizations
- **pyproject.toml**: Add an initial `pyproject.toml` to future-proof the package installation.

### Cleanup

- Basic clean up reducing code duplications and recursions
